  <brief_title>Oral Rivaroxaban in Children With Venous Thrombosis</brief_title>
  <acronym>EINSTEINJunior</acronym>
  <official_title>30-day, Single-arm Study of the Safety, Efficacy and the Pharmacokinetic and Pharmacodynamic Properties of Oral Rivaroxaban in Children With Various Manifestations of Venous Thrombosis</official_title>
